data.description: Buyers Rebate offered, restrictions apply and must be ratified by 11/27/2023. Nestled in the serene Lakes at Donegal Springs, this stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence presents a charming blend of contemporary comfort and natural beauty. Built in 2006, this meticulously maintained home exudes timeless elegance and offers an inviting sanctuary for modern living.   Step inside and be greeted by an abundance of natural light that effortlessly illuminates the spacious living areas. The open-concept design seamlessly integrates the living room, kitchen, and dining area, creating an ideal setting for both relaxation and entertainment. With ample living space, a spacious backyard, and convenient access to local amenities, this property presents an ideal blend of modern living and tranquil surroundings.
